      • isQuestionSetEnabledByPublicId

        boolean isQuestionSetEnabledByPublicId(java.lang.String questionSetPublicId)
        Returns true if QuestionSetSelection is enabled by questionSetPublicId according to this offering. This will be true if either the offering explicitly lists the question set as being enabled, or if the offering does not mention the question set at all. Returns false only if the offering explicitly lists the question set as being disabled.
        Parameters:
        questionSetPublicId - the publicId of the question set
        Returns:
        Returns true if this offering is enabled for the given QuestionSet.
